  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      An observational two-center case-control study exploring the clinical impact of
      double-carbapenem use in a population of critically il patients with severe
      carbapenem-resistant Klebsiella pneumoniae infection
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
